Common Implementation Paths

1. Own runtime MDX components Define mdxComponents in the docs app that renders your pages. @inth/docs intentionally does not export prebuilt UI components. 2. Convert MDX for agents Use @inth/docs/convert with @inth/docs/remark to flatten authored MDX into markdown that works in LLM bundles and search indexes. 3. Generate and query search Generate static search JSON with @inth/docs/search/node , query it with @inth/docs/search , and add a provider entrypoint such as @inth/docs/search/vercel only for explicit answer requests.

