Methodology

docs site. @inth/docs Shared docs infrastructure package framework-neutral MDX-to-markdown conversion, LLM bundles, linting, static search, and answer helpers. Teams that want to own the app shell and runtime components while reusing one docs pipeline across sites, agents, search APIs, and internal tools. These tools are not mutually exclusive. A site framework can own the public docs experience while @inth/docs owns conversion, validation, search artifacts, and agent-facing bundles.

